text: Olwakhwaruma Musa khubandu bebe,(nababoolela mbu) istulile tsimbabaasi tsia Nyasaye tsili khwinywe. Olwa khwabahabina okhurula khubandu ba Firauni, ababahelesinjia eshinyasio eshilulu, abasinzanga Abana benyu abasiani nenibalekha abeshikhasi, toto mukano kalimwo amarechekho amakhongo okhurula khu Nyasaye wenyu
